WEBVTT

00:00:27.150 --> 00:00:30.917
People are reacting differently

00:00:30.941 --> 00:00:32.307
to the climate crisis

00:00:32.331 --> 00:00:34.948
in the midst of these
other great challenges

00:00:34.972 --> 00:00:38.268
that have taken over our awareness,

00:00:38.292 --> 00:00:39.460
appropriately.

00:00:40.175 --> 00:00:43.852
One reason is something
that you mentioned.

00:00:43.876 --> 00:00:47.465
People get the fact
that when scientists are warning us

00:00:47.489 --> 00:00:49.677
in ever more dire terms

00:00:49.701 --> 00:00:51.827
and setting their hair
on fire, so to speak,

00:00:51.851 --> 00:00:54.812
it's best to listen
to what they're saying,

00:00:54.836 --> 00:00:59.254
and I think that lesson
has begun to sink in in a new way.

00:00:59.278 --> 00:01:01.372
Another similarity, by the way,